# SAGU

## Setting Variables

var variable_name = 12


# Doing math

var twenty = 12 + 8


## Logical operations

var istrue = 12 + 8 < 20


## Flow Control

if condition {block} elif condition {block} else {block}

or

if condition {
    var block = 12
}
elseif condition {
    var block = 32
}
else {
    var block = 45
}

## While Loops

